Let modules include other modules via a `<module>.mojl.json` file.

Static site building feature with lodash templates.

Feature for merging css and scss into the same file

Option to set a pattern or function for determining whether to timestamp a given file during path rewriting, since not all files should be timestamped. For example, files imported with sass instead of css shouldn't be timestamped, because they're filesystem paths, not URLs.




